 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:26:50.000Z","msg":"唔係啊手足，正因為我地見到五個月黎冇出路所以先要革新新方向啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:27:35.000Z","msg":"咁有咩新方向 林鄭落台？邊個上？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:29:47.000Z","msg":"可以再討論，但第一步一定係林鄭落台<br />\n初步方向可以係民選政府<br />\n不如手足你又講下持續現況點先可以得到勝利?"},{"pid":"9344ebe3ed4048f5a35c1fa33c0e65817887c9eb","tid":1711381,"uid":328448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:30:03.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n4/10"},{"pid":"7d29303dcbb51324dc4b438c4657b29731955497","tid":1711381,"uid":328448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"39a78b39e5e2f7d450a82c9675d68796783fe9e4","tid":1711381,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87f16cd23b01e2daff34856cdc81a8b3c51dfa7f","tid":1711381,"uid":328448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7055ffb2202b4c9ae40e11bf4c6db99893088a4a","tid":1711381,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d83d3960d8bbce907e5fe6133096fdc4d8bf2a8","tid":1711381,"uid":328448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:26:50.000Z","msg":"唔係啊手足，正因為我地見到五個月黎冇出路所以先要革新新方向啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:27:35.000Z","msg":"咁有咩新方向 林鄭落台？邊個上？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:29:47.000Z","msg":"可以再討論，但第一步一定係林鄭落台<br />\n初步方向可以係民選政府<br />\n不如手足你又講下持續現況點先可以得到勝利?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:32:18.000Z","msg":"民選政府咪即係第5個demands <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你無第5個demands點有民選政府<br />\n<br />\n方法其實好簡單 無限期罷工/ 真暴動<br />\n只有經濟牌先可以贏到<br />\n前者相對好d"},{"pid":"98aea3423964b9cb6b581be42c64292902378b96","tid":1711381,"uid":90290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:32:32.000Z","msg":"認同要推翻目前政府<br />\n但我地一個冇大台為前提既革命<br />\n係冇人組到所謂新政府<br />\n所以要推翻較難<br />\n睇